{"lastModified":1775746179697,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::c034eca0-3a1a-11f0-acbd-29907c34ceff","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: \nSummer 2026:  Italy - Sardinia, Italy - Sicily, Italy - South (mainland)\nWinter 2025/2026: Bermuda, British Virgin Islands, Cuba, Dominican Republic, Leeward Islands, The Bahamas, Trinidad & Tobago, US Virgin Islands, Windward Islands\n\nStep aboard Sunreef 70 ANKAWER IV, a sophisticated sailing catamaran designed for both relaxation and adventure on the open sea. With a smart galley-down layout, this vessel maximizes the saloon space, creating a bright and airy environment ideal for socializing or unwinding.\n\nAccommodating up to eight guests, ANKAWER IV features three elegant guest cabins and a spacious master suite, all thoughtfully appointed for comfort and privacy. Dedicated crew quarters ensure seamless, discreet service throughout your voyage.\n\nNavigation is effortless with helm stations both on the flybridge and inside the saloon, allowing for smooth sailing in all conditions. Whether you’re lounging on deck, taking in the views from the flybridge, or enjoying quiet moments in your private cabin, ANKAWER IV offers a refined, unforgettable experience at sea.","blueprint":{"name":"ANKAWER VI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c034eca0-3a1a-11f0-acbd-29907c34ceff::assets::393d9d80-3a1c-11f0-8c3b-61a3b6b09053/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c034eca0-3a1a-11f0-acbd-29907c34ceff::assets::393c3df0-3a1c-11f0-8c3b-61a3b6b09053/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c034eca0-3a1a-11f0-acbd-29907c34ceff::assets::393cb320-3a1c-11f0-8c3b-61a3b6b09053/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c034eca0-3a1a-11f0-acbd-29907c34ceff::assets::393cda30-3a1c-11f0-8c3b-61a3b6b09053/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c034eca0-3a1a-11f0-acbd-29907c34ceff::assets::3940f8e1-3a1c-11f0-8c3c-61a3b6b09053/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c034eca0-3